President Tzervôstuhr of Travakstan gets dethroned and flees to Darkwood, a shelter for dethroned dictators. Kiekeboe buys the pink Rolls of the ex-president, but he wants it back at all costs and also Mon Crott, the leader of the Travakstan opposition, is chasing the car for his own.
name: De Roze Rolls

description: Kiekeboe sees a mermaid popping up everywhere, Charlotte discovers a body and Fanny goes to Portugal for modeling. And then Franz Mann, the project developer, Paul Ster, the brother of the deceased, and Ann Gora, the lady with the dangerous lips, appear and nothing will ever be the same.
name: Gedonder Om De Bliksem

description: By the order of Van de Kasseien, Kiekeboe must elicit compromising negatives from the blackmailer Karel Keizer. When Kiekeboe also gets involved with the kidnapping of a famous pianist, also the friend of Fanny, the ground gets really hot beneath his feet.
name: Schiet Niet Op De Pianist

description: A disappeared Miss Stokvis and a protest action of Fanny against medical tests on animals, set Kiekeboe on the trail of a mad doctor. He has developed a medicine against aging. The doctor wants to poison the whole population with the Huppeldepupvirus, which makes you age faster, and thus expand his client database.
name: Het Stokvis-incident

description: During her job in a flower congratulation service, Fanny discovers bags of cocaine are smuggled out of the South American country El Tondzon. Those bags are put in folkloristic puppets which coffee manufacturer San T. Koffie gives to old people as a present. San T. Koffie is in the hands of a familiar face in new clothes: Thimothea Triangl, still mad for power and money.
name: Zeg Het Met Bloemen

description: A change of photocameras for the Epcot-centre in Florida, the bizarre Holy Hamburger Movement, a wreckage of a ship with juwels of an oil sheik and the new friend of Fanny who transforms into a shark: these seem like elements for a Kiekeboe-story by a beginning storyteller.
name: Haaiman

description: The graveyard where the vampires live, is getting dismantled. Mona threatens Kiekeboe with a vampire kiss, if he doesn't prevent the dismantlement. During a reception Mona's friend will try to steal the building permit.
name: De Kus Van Mona

description: With his new firm Van de Kasseien wants to keep his affaire with his secretary Suzy a secret for his wife. Kiekeboe is hired to sell the 'light' product, the holes in the cheese. Amazingly, he manages to do that. A rival company wants to stop it.
name: Het Gat In De Kaas

description: Fanny and her new friend Ken explore, together with archeologist W. Ten Schap, the tunnels beneath the broken down castle Ter Goude in Gouda. During their exploration, they stumble unto a counterfeiting network.
name: De Zes Sterren

description:
The Crack

With Itachi having stopped Kabuto, it’s time for the Edotensei warriors to finally be returned to the afterlife! This means that Itachi’s time on earth will also be coming to an end. How will Sasuke deal with losing his brother once again? And what dark tricks does Madara have up his sleeve?!

description: Citro's an all-too-human android boy who lives with his "grandfather," an old mechanic, and Corona, the mechanic's granddaughter. When warring factions battle it out at his home, a powerful device implants itself in Citro, making him both more powerful and the target of evil forces. Tragedy propels Citro and Corona on a quest, accompanied by their new ally Tera, the broomstick- flying, techno-witch.
name: Vol. 1

description: Continuing their journey, Citro and his companions arrive at the port city of Elrain. Once there, they are surrounded by enemies and Corona, Citro's human sister, is taken hostage. The young android boy knows how to amass the power he'll need to save her, but can he live with what it's going to cost him?

Gorgeous Kiri is a popular television personality with legions of fans who drool over her every move. But her crafty cousin Taku is the only guy who can claim to know what she truly desires. Will these two cousins learn to tame their tempers and play nice…or is that hardly the point?

Absolute Monarch Syndrome teases and terrorizes with a tale of secret temptations and shocking surprises! When a series of childhood games takes a turn for the perverse, there’s no telling who will make their humble servant bow down and kiss the ground beneath their feet!

  • Ch 1: A Strange Pair
  • Ch 2: Her Mark
  • Ch 3: Kinaco
  • Ch 4: Secret Desire
  • Ch 5: Your True Self
  • Ch 6: The Birth of the Absolute Monarch Part 1
  • Ch 7: The Birth of the Absolute Monarch Part 2

description:
Shige feels he’s the luckiest guy in the world. His girl Mayu is short, cute and… uh, “well-endowed.” In fact, Shige’s tantamount to worshipping her voluptuous front, but it turns out, Mayu wants more than just a quick fondle. Meanwhile, Souta is down in the dumps after his date stands him up at the beach. Good thing he’s met Yui who works at the beach café, she’ll do anything to cheer him up.

Stuck in an unhappy marriage, Mr. Shimokogawa gives his new neighbor, the sexy Ms. Amano, an offer she can’t refuse. On the other hand, poor Nishino’s first sexual encounter with Maya came to a disastrously “pre-mature” end. So when he meets her again years later, he thinks he’s been given a chance to rectify his failure. And then there’s this two kids at a college drama club who enact their own racy version of Romeo and Juliet.

But wait, there’s more! This collection of naughty vignettes from creator Michiyoshi Kuon features just about every fetishist’s far-out fantasy. Waitresses, office girls, college sweethearts, childhood sweethearts, office sweethearts, one-night stands, extra-marital affairs, girls with dual personalities, girls with glasses, “well-endowed” girls… name it, everything is within these pages!

  • The Girlfriend Strikes Back
  • From Now On You're My Servant!
  • mermaid of the Evening Calm
  • A Humble Juliet
  • Crime, Punishment, and Nectar
  • Imbalanced Lovers
  • An Appropriate Relationship
  • Vroom Vroom Honey
  • Cherry Petal
  • The Boyfriend Strikes Back

description:
A young man trying to get into college...

A shut-in living out her fantasies online...

A young couple in need of excitement...

A clumsy girl trying to find her place in the world...

Spring. A time for study, for play, for work, for rebirth...for sex. Yuu is a young man with one dream: to get into the same collage as his lovely girlfriend, Saki. Unfortunately, he failed the entrance exam, while Saki got in! With Saki waiting for him, Yuu is even more determined to make it into college tofulfill their dreams. There's only one problem: how can he focus and study when Saki refuses to let up on the sex?

Aren't you curious? Like the characters in the story. this manga just wants to know one thing "How Good Was I?" Don't disappoint it! Read and find out for yourself!

  • How Good Was I?
    • Part One
    • Part Two
    • Part Three
  • Cyber Rabbit
  • Excitement On the Roof
  • Imp - Imp -
  • Don't Mind If I Do!
  • Athletic Error
  • Good For Something!
  • With My Cousin
name: Vol. 1

description:
What starts off as a simple crush for office worker Aogi takes a turn for the kinky when the beautiful and busty Marie, Aogi’s secret love and the new hire, asks Aogi to “Please be my master.” There's only one problem…what exactly does a "master" do? Battling with thoughts of love and lust, Aogi begins to get all the wrong ideas…or right ideas the more he begins to command Marie: "Off with your panties!"

How To Make Him My Master presents a fresh new take on the master and slave relationship. Full of laughs, kinky sex, and heart, you'll be sure to enjoy the blossoming and unusual romance between Aoki and Marie.

  • How To Make Him My Master
  • How To Spend Time With My Master
  • How To Heal My Master
